            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Indelviae <expan><abbr>T</abbr><ex>iti</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>fil</abbr><ex>iae</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/>Valerillae <lb n="3"/>flaminicae <lb n="4"/>perpetuae <lb n="5"/>quae pro eo honore <lb n="6"/>statuam argenteam cum <lb n="7"/>basi ex HS L <expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>ilibus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>n</abbr><ex>ummum</ex></expan> <lb n="8"/>in basilica posuit <lb n="9"/>ob quam munificentiam <lb n="10"/>ordo sanctissimus <lb n="11"/>statuam ei ponendam <lb n="12"/>de publico decrevit <lb n="13"/>quae honore contenta <lb n="14"/>inpendium remisit
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Nomen gentile Indelvius ist Hapax.</p>
            </div>
